  "time_ut": 1659071648,
  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u0d94\u0db8\u0dd2\u0d9a\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0ddd\u0db1\u0dca \u0d8b\u0db4 \u0db4\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0db7\u0dda\u0daf\u0dba \u0dc4\u0dd8\u0daf \u0dc3\u0ddb\u0dbd\u0dc0\u0dbd\u0da7 \u0dc4\u0dcf\u0db1\u0dd2 \u0d9a\u0dbb\u0db1\u0dc0\u0dcf",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The omicron subtype damages heart cells",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Portuguese medical researchers say that the 'BA5' mutation, which has been identified as a sub-variant of the Covid-19 omicron mutation, is a dangerous mutation that spreads rapidly and that 'BA5' damages heart cells.",
        "Regarding the 'BA5' virus, Portuguese medical researchers have done some extensive research and they have now discovered accordingly. The total number of 'Covid 19' patients reported from Portugal is 5,337,121. Deaths are reported as 24,587. The number of people who have recovered is 4,237,853.",
        "'Omicron' was able to lessen the severity of the 'Covid 19' epidemic, reduce the number of hospitalized 'Covid 19' patients and deaths, but the sub-mutations born from the 'Omicron' mutation have taken a horrible form.",
        "Currently, the world has shown an increase in the number of people infected with Covid-19 due to the sub-variants of the 'Omicron' mutation. Several sub-varieties have been identified, of which 'BA5' is considered to be the most dangerous sub-variety.",
        "The World Health Organization has also warned that the number of infected people being hospitalized is increasing and more and more deaths have started to be reported due to the effect of the 'BA5' sub mutation.",
        "The total number of infected with 'Covid 19' is 579,780,429. Total deaths are reported as 6,414,615. 549,638,534 people have been infected with 'Covid-19' and fully recovered."
      ],
